</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_261" id="130v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Techant czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> oder
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> official etc. </ab>
